    "In this study, product attributes refer to the inherent properties of a product.",
    "Using robotic vacuum cleaners as an example, attributes such as lifespan, suction power, and noise level are considered product attributes.",
    "The attribute-grained preference analysis task is aimed at identifying aspects that users like or dislike and comparing them with competing products.",
    "Moreover, one filtered genuine review C = [w1, w2, • • •, wi, • • • wm] consists of m words, and some of the words{wi1,",
